EpsExtensions - IO adapter for Solr - Getting Started



* Introduction

	This is a simple getting started guide to using the Eps Extension IO adapter for Solr

* Steps by Step

	To configure and use Solr Output Adapter, follow the steps below.


* Dependencies

	<<Step 1:>> Add dependencies to application distribution package POM file

	...

+-----+
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.ericsson.oss.services</groupId>
    <artifactId>exteps-io-solr</artifactId>
    <version>${project.version}</version>
    <type>tar.gz</type>
</dependency>
+-----+



